# MIDINotificationMessageID.msgThruConnectionsChanged

**Case**

The system created or disposed of a persistent MIDI Thru connection.

## Declaration

```swift
case msgThruConnectionsChanged
```

## Discussion

This type has no data.

## Change Types

- **MIDINotificationMessageID.msgSetupChanged**: Some aspect of the current MIDI setup changed.
- **MIDINotificationMessageID.msgObjectAdded**: The system added a device, entity, or endpoint.
- **MIDINotificationMessageID.msgObjectRemoved**: The system removed a device, entity, or endpoint.
- **MIDINotificationMessageID.msgPropertyChanged**: An object’s property value changed.
- **MIDINotificationMessageID.msgSerialPortOwnerChanged**: The system changed a serial port owner.
- **MIDINotificationMessageID.msgIOError**: A driver I/O error occurred.
